node.text: #FlashbackFriday to 2000 when my #HeyKandi album just dropped. This was a time when people actually went to the store to buy cd’s & i had to do a promo tour to do meet & greets for autograph signings. How many of y’all remember those days?! Now everybody just streams & downloads everything. 💿💿💿
